{"tid":1809153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新城市廣場外圍走火通道經常上鎖","createTime":"2020-01-03T01:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:58:36.000Z","uid":10540,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"491c319439db7b9aad080cf2d05a9f107744b4bb","tid":1809153,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/80975605_2664226793633102_6213276509902209024_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ohc=0d3nffPQbq8AQntPjH70EuosxDk9eP4gYrp-NBkXSt19W_Nd-LxbMDdDg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=029563f73471a77dc6ae078c4c266338&amp;oe=5EB2E083\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F80975605_2664226793633102_6213276509902209024_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ohc%3D0d3nffPQbq8AQntPjH70EuosxDk9eP4gYrp-NBkXSt19W_Nd-LxbMDdDg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D029563f73471a77dc6ae078c4c266338%26oe%3D5EB2E083&h=6bffab67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場一期外圍的走火通道經常上鎖，其後管理公司職員才解鎖。而市民多次反映甚至聯絡消防作出投訴，發展商仍然不理會。<br />\n<br />\n過程：<br />\n<strong>第一次 星期一 12月30日</strong><br />\n12:30 打電話及電郵去 沙田消防局投訴大家樂走火通道地下鐵鏈鎖門。<br />\n消防局回覆：巡查後發現冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二次12月31日</strong><br />\n16:26 打電話及電郵去 沙田消防局再投訴返第一次嘅嘢。<br />\n21:52 消防符Sir巡查後回覆：當時去到唔見有，話冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n接聽完消防符Sir電話，聽完佢一輪廢⋯，真係火都嚟，我即刻換衫沖落去再睇，一樣係鎖住冇改，立即打電話俾沙田消防局，符Sir接聽電話，佢想推我⋯⋯。我話你要即刻嚟我喺度等你，我唔會離開，我仲叫阿Sir，求下你救下我啦⋯⋯火燭鎖埋死人㗎佢局住要開車過嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81442387_2668408066548308_6185382153308602368_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_ohc=yJiKiBOgV38AQlyksBnnUPQwc_IhZmnnMPWb81499H4rP9mxjnJMwNQzg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=db25520be3fa246062f33837ee0861cc&amp;oe=5E69D06A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81442387_2668408066548308_6185382153308602368_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_ohc%3DyJiKiBOgV38AQlyksBnnUPQwc_IhZmnnMPWb81499H4rP9mxjnJMwNQzg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Ddb25520be3fa246062f33837ee0861cc%26oe%3D5E69D06A&h=ec929716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23:30 沙田消防局車到達<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年1月1日</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81272511_2668407693215012_5866050471562575872_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ohc=ltb96DzZTlYAQkntKLFWWYVTFzMVn7iC4799iZHV9ByPsqWNvfTozpyJA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=ef7083e90a0640e2e50258caf36bbcdb&amp;oe=5E6BF974\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81272511_2668407693215012_5866050471562575872_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ohc%3Dltb96DzZTlYAQkntKLFWWYVTFzMVn7iC4799iZHV9ByPsqWNvfTozpyJA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Def7083e90a0640e2e50258caf36bbcdb%26oe%3D5E6BF974&h=5a735528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n00:00 消防嚟到新鴻基職員攞鎖匙解除鐵鏈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81274824_2668406186548496_6731585230378893312_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ohc=NYjwfO3HFGYAQlN8Nt_uOYTzqiHvwZLeP6o0DomOJBcfLMhpC3IaUAXWg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=4ef1a30a878e6a34c1cf31ef874736da&amp;oe=5EAC72B8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81274824_2668406186548496_6731585230378893312_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ohc%3DNYjwfO3HFGYAQlN8Nt_uOYTzqiHvwZLeP6o0DomOJBcfLMhpC3IaUAXWg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D4ef1a30a878e6a34c1cf31ef874736da%26oe%3D5EAC72B8&h=fc286694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81154719_2668406933215088_4019799130871169024_n.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ohc=2HpGbdfFT5MAQkhLIi-WkqflngKfMmHzoCQZJLys-x2-g0vf_MWbiMo3A&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=d79dd3a765d5ab07e9383eb2a6909f94&amp;oe=5EA625D1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81154719_2668406933215088_4019799130871169024_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ohc%3D2HpGbdfFT5MAQkhLIi-WkqflngKfMmHzoCQZJLys-x2-g0vf_MWbiMo3A%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dd79dd3a765d5ab07e9383eb2a6909f94%26oe%3D5EA625D1&h=9d61563c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11:08 吃完早餐後約去百步梯睇，新鴻基職員全部用鐵鏈上鎖頭🔒有關消防出口通道。<br />\n<br />\n對於新鴻基有關安排，漠視消防條例，罔顧市民安全，多次反映甚至聯絡消防作出投訴，新地仍然不理會，目無法紀，對居住在新城市三期/沙田廣場/偉華中心住戶及一期公眾通道市民構成嚴重危險，漠視市民生命安危。"},{"pid":"9045c24b5ede29e63005126dd83eab3db1cb3d18","tid":1809153,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"Sell HK"},{"pid":"9f96fbb07a5b44cb0c013476dcdf324b15ccc140","tid":1809153,"uid":119408,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n報ICAC<br />\n懷疑消防同地產公司勾結<br />\n<br />\n唔好理ICAC有冇用先 開咗file Sell HK同消防就有所顧忌"},{"pid":"8068054fdd7db2bd12de95e36af5fdb5b82898c1","tid":1809153,"uid":119408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f96fbb07a5b44cb0c013476dcdf324b15ccc140","tid":1809153,"uid":119408,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n報ICAC<br />\n懷疑消防同地產公司勾結<br />\n<br />\n唔好理ICAC有冇用先 開咗file Sell HK同消防就有所顧忌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:37:53.000Z","msg":"撳錯不推文 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d278e9c6e8ceb0401f0d9eed47f34482c4cbbc","tid":1809153,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"Sell HK"},{"pid":"acbb2dab17bbfdb463034211eb20856310737e5f","tid":1809153,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0cf1603dfa292bdcc28595f6a3e119e05e104ba","tid":1809153,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"用申訴專員公署去告果個消防局指揮<br />\n<br />\n不過要你實名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都開過名啦...係煩啲"},{"pid":"100af0a145c0e727cad4875cdd2aa3c92dd34d0f","tid":1809153,"uid":237260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci